{"tid":162923,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"結婚係唔係必要？","createTime":"2017-03-19T15:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-19T15:59:53.000Z","uid":14319,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a19768e74b3a6d7d1ba4c17020ebfd400ce9510","tid":162923,"uid":14319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:14:05.000Z","msg":"其實大家認為結婚係唔係人生入面一定要有既階段？因為我自己就覺得無所謂 想問下其他人係點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n認同=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔認同=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7617672b82fce004877098492b6997e505b96354","tid":162923,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:17:09.000Z","msg":"其實結婚唔係一紙婚書咁簡單<br />\n仲係保障<br />\n唔止係心理上<br />\n仲有財政上<br />\n例如報税 買樓填名 遺產 之類"},{"pid":"c339c035c604c0bec51171bdf35d0051a913ee54","tid":162923,"uid":14319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:29:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實結婚唔係一紙婚書咁簡單<br />\n仲係保障<br />\n唔止係心理上<br />\n仲有財政上<br />\n例如報税 買樓填名 遺產 之類</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n所以我覺得結婚好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b38bba84e4da369ffa6729b11bbbd99f03e440","tid":162923,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:31:08.000Z","msg":"除咗死係必要之外<br />\n<br />\n其他你喜歡點都得"},{"pid":"a13ac3c20b87d37a6adeb5fc48379df8a680b07e","tid":162923,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:31:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實結婚唔係一紙婚書咁簡單<br />\n仲係保障<br />\n唔止係心理上<br />\n仲有財政上<br />\n例如報税 買樓填名 遺產 之類</blockquote><br />\n說穿了其實雙方唔信任對方<br />\n要靠法律保障自己<br />\n垃圾關係"},{"pid":"d6b0b3a04ca94e28fa710a7da752a898c90b001f","tid":162923,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:31:45.000Z","msg":"簽個名就算啦<br />\n要搞大龍鳳小丑show就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{